The paper discusses the integration of multisensory observations, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The study focuses on audio-visual (AV) conflict resolution, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and signal processing (cs.SD). The paper also mentions the use of robots in real-world environments, which falls under robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the study involves human perception and cognition, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
